summary:
shout out to all the awesome unseen creators in the phandom. 
shout out to all the writers, who work their butts off researching...
body:
shout out to all the awesome unseen creators in the phandom.

shout out to all the writers, who work their butts off researching and revising and writing for just a couple of notes.

shout out to all the artists, traditional or digital, who work hard to create a style or a piece they like and are proud of only to get a few likes.

shout out to all the editors and gif makers, who try new things and make new colorings and who don’t get recognized nearly enough.

shout out to anyone who’s posted one of their own creative works and didn’t the feedback they deserved.

i see you. you’re important to this phandom, even if it might not seem like it or you yourself don’t think so. i appreciate your creativity and work and i’m so, so proud of you.
